OL,3,CPrison to be shut for a further three
OL,4,Cyears due to discovery of radioactive
OL,5,Cgas
OL,7,FA category C men's prison in Devon is
OL,8,Fto remain shut for a further three
OL,9,Fyears, following the discovery of the
OL,10,Fpresence of radioactive gas two years
OL,11,Fago.
OL,13,FHMP Dartmoor was first evacuated in
OL,14,F2023 after high levels of radon ` a
OL,15,Fcolourless, odourless radioactive gas
OL,16,F- were found, leading to around 400
OL,17,Finmates being temporarily removed from
OL,18,Fthe site.
