OL,3,CPrison to be shut for a further three
OL,4,Cyears due to discovery of radioactive
OL,5,Cgas
OL,7,FThe Grade II listed site then recorded
OL,8,Ffurther high levels of the gas shortly
OL,9,Fafter inmates began to return in July
OL,10,F2024, leading to 175 prisoners being
OL,11,Fremoved later that month.
OL,13,FNow, the Prison Officers' Association
OL,14,F(POA) has said it understands that the
OL,15,Fprison will be shut to inmates for a
OL,16,Ffurther three years.
OL,18,FSarah Rigby, the South West
OL,19,Frepresentative for the POA, said it
OL,20,Fwas the latest estimate from Prison
OL,21,FService officials.
