OL,7,FShe said that most of the prison's 300
OL,8,Fmembers of staff had been transferred
OL,9,Fto other sites including Exeter and
OL,10,FChannings Wood, and that the Ministry
OL,11,Fof Justice (MoJ) has agreed to pay
OL,12,Ftravel costs for them for the next
OL,13,Fthree years.
OL,15,FAlthough the POA wishes for the prison
OL,16,Fto reopen, she added that she
OL,17,Fquestions how many of the staff will
OL,18,Fwant to return to HMP Dartmoor.
OL,20,FWhat is radon and how has it been
OL,21,Ffound in HMP Dartmoor?
