OL,4,Cyears due to discovery of radioactive
OL,5,Cgas
OL,7,FHMP Dartmoor was built in the early
OL,8,F19th century to hold French prisoners
OL,9,Fduring the Napoleonic Wars, and was
OL,10,Fslated for closure in 2023. But that
OL,11,Fdecision was reversed in 2019 in the
OL,12,Fface of rising prisoner numbers.
OL,14,FSince the discovery of the gas, the
OL,15,FGovernment has been forced to release
OL,16,Fthousands of prisoners across England
OL,17,Fand Wales due to overcrowding in the
OL,18,Fprison system.
