OL,5,Cgas
OL,7,FBut even with the lower 40% automatic
OL,8,Frelease, it is expected to only fix
OL,9,Fthe problem for 18 months.
OL,11,FResponding to the union's claim that
OL,12,Fthe prison may be shut for a further
OL,13,Fthree years, a spokesperson for the
OL,14,FPrison Service said: "After close
OL,15,Fmonitoring of the situation at HMP
OL,16,FDartmoor, we took the decision to
OL,17,Ftemporarily close the site.
OL,19,F"We continue to take advice from
OL,20,Fspecialists to explore how it can be
OL,21,Freopened as quickly as possible."
